#PThis God is a spirit that lives amongst us within this very Forest. 
Some call it Gaia others God/Godess, yet no one is certain. 
It's form changes upon the moon, sun, even it's surroundings. Once an 
animal like form that can camouflaged to it's surroundings. Then at night 
it'll become a walking translucent spirit that you can barely see except 
under the moons rays. This spirit never speaks and just the sight of it leaves 
you in awe. This spirit's apart of you as it is apart of all of us and all 
life it's self. It gives and then can quickly take it away draining your energy 
in order to create life making things grow or to heal ones wounds. 
Sometimes, just sometimes, if you're chosen this spirit will bring you back to 
life.#n
~
