#gYou're standing in the middle of a beautiful Rain Forest. 
Birds fly by peacefully whistling their happy tune. Animals scurry about, enjoying
a beautiful day in the sun. While others hide in the trees or lower grounds, 
camouflaged by the shadows and hidden brush, awaiting the night, to resume their 
nocturnal behavior. As night begins to fall many colorful crickets hide amongst 
beautiful glowing flowers, chirping their cheerful songs of joy to the end of 
this peaceful day. Suddenly, something above catches you're eye. Woah, what do ya know. 
It's a Siamese looking monkey hanging upside down from a massive tree. The monkey 
throws an orange colored fruit at the base of the tree, right next to an ancient stone. 
Almost as if he was trying to direct your attention to the engraved markings that adorn 
this moss covered relic. #p{{#Ptype look stone to read discription#p}}#n
